9745static int32_T c1_div_nzp_s32(SFc1_GCU_Model_genCodeInstanceStruct



9746  *chartInstance, int32_T c1_numerator, int32_T c1_denominator, uint32_T



9747  c1_ssid_src_loc, int32_T c1_offset_src_loc, int32_T c1_length_src_loc)



9748{



9749  int32_T c1_quotient;



9750  uint32_T c1_absNumerator;



9751  uint32_T c1_absDenominator;



9752  boolean_T c1_quotientNeedsNegation;



9753  uint32_T c1_tempAbsQuotient;



9754  (void)chartInstance;



9755  (void)c1_ssid_src_loc;



9756  (void)c1_offset_src_loc;



9757  (void)c1_length_src_loc;



9758  if (c1_numerator < 0) {



9759    c1_absNumerator = ~(uint32_T)c1_numerator + 1U;



9760  } else {



9761    c1_absNumerator = (uint32_T)c1_numerator;



9762  }



9763



9764  if (c1_denominator < 0) {



9765    c1_absDenominator = ~(uint32_T)c1_denominator + 1U;



9766  } else {



9767    c1_absDenominator = (uint32_T)c1_denominator;



9768  }



9769



9770  c1_quotientNeedsNegation = ((c1_numerator < 0) != (c1_denominator < 0));



9771  c1_tempAbsQuotient = c1_absNumerator / c1_absDenominator;



9772  if (c1_quotientNeedsNegation) {



9773    c1_quotient = -(int32_T)c1_tempAbsQuotient;



9774  } else {



9775    c1_quotient = (int32_T)c1_tempAbsQuotient;



9776  }



9777



9778  return c1_quotient;



9779}

12749    }

12758    if (ssGetUserData(S)!= NULL) {

12760    }



12761



12762    ssSetUserData(S,NULL);



12763  }



12764}

12804      (sim_mode_is_rtw_gen(S), sim_mode_is_modelref_sim(S), sim_mode_is_external

12820      (),infoStruct,1,15);

12829      ssSetInputPortOptimOpts(S, 7, SS_REUSABLE_AND_LOCAL);

12832        infoStruct,1,9);

12834        infoStruct,1,3);

12841      }



12842    }

12847        ssSetInputPortOptimizeInIR(S, inPortIdx, 1U);



12848      }



12849    }



12850



12851    sf_set_rtw_dwork_info(S,sf_get_instance_specialization(),infoStruct,1);



12852    sf_register_codegen_names_for_scoped_functions_defined_by_chart(S);

12854  } else {



12855  }



12856

12858  ssSetChecksum0(S,(769858010U));



12859  ssSetChecksum1(S,(2540324675U));

12875static void mdlStart_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(SimStruct *S)



12876{



12877  SFc1_GCU_Model_genCodeInstanceStruct *chartInstance;



12878  chartInstance = (SFc1_GCU_Model_genCodeInstanceStruct *)utMalloc(sizeof



12879    (SFc1_GCU_Model_genCodeInstanceStruct));



12880  if (chartInstance==NULL) {



12881    sf_mex_error_message("Could not allocate memory for chart instance.");



12882  }



12883



12884  memset(chartInstance, 0, sizeof(SFc1_GCU_Model_genCodeInstanceStruct));



12885  chartInstance->chartInfo.chartInstance = chartInstance;



12886  chartInstance->chartInfo.isEMLChart = 0;



12887  chartInstance->chartInfo.chartInitialized = 0;



12888  chartInstance->chartInfo.sFunctionGateway =



12889    sf_opaque_gateway_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



12890  chartInstance->chartInfo.initializeChart =



12891    sf_opaque_initialize_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



12892  chartInstance->chartInfo.terminateChart =



12893    sf_opaque_terminate_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



12894  chartInstance->chartInfo.enableChart = sf_opaque_enable_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



12895  chartInstance->chartInfo.disableChart = sf_opaque_disable_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



12896  chartInstance->chartInfo.getSimState =



12897    sf_opaque_get_sim_state_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



12898  chartInstance->chartInfo.setSimState =



12899    sf_opaque_set_sim_state_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



12900  chartInstance->chartInfo.getSimStateInfo =



12901    sf_get_sim_state_info_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



12902  chartInstance->chartInfo.zeroCrossings = NULL;



12903  chartInstance->chartInfo.outputs = NULL;



12904  chartInstance->chartInfo.derivatives = NULL;



12905  chartInstance->chartInfo.mdlRTW = mdlRTW_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



12906  chartInstance->chartInfo.mdlStart = mdlStart_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



12907  chartInstance->chartInfo.mdlSetWorkWidths =



12908    mdlSetWorkWidths_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



12909  chartInstance->chartInfo.callGetHoverDataForMsg =



12910    sf_opaque_get_hover_data_for_msg;



12911  chartInstance->chartInfo.extModeExec = NULL;



12912  chartInstance->chartInfo.restoreLastMajorStepConfiguration = NULL;



12913  chartInstance->chartInfo.restoreBeforeLastMajorStepConfiguration = NULL;



12914  chartInstance->chartInfo.storeCurrentConfiguration = NULL;



12915  chartInstance->chartInfo.callAtomicSubchartUserFcn = NULL;



12916  chartInstance->chartInfo.callAtomicSubchartAutoFcn = NULL;



12917  chartInstance->chartInfo.callAtomicSubchartEventFcn = NULL;



12918  chartInstance->chartInfo.debugInstance = sfGlobalDebugInstanceStruct;



12919  chartInstance->S = S;



12920  sf_init_ChartRunTimeInfo(S, &(chartInstance->chartInfo), false, 0);



12921  init_dsm_address_info(chartInstance);



12922  init_simulink_io_address(chartInstance);



12923  if (!sim_mode_is_rtw_gen(S)) {



12924    init_test_point_mapping_info(S);



12925  }



12926



12927  chart_debug_initialization(S,1);



12928  mdl_start_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(chartInstance);



12929}

12931void c1_GCU_Model_genCode_method_dispatcher(SimStruct *S, int_T method, void



12932  *data)



12933{



12934  switch (method) {



12935   case SS_CALL_MDL_START:



12936    mdlStart_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(S);



12937    break;



12938



12939   case SS_CALL_MDL_SET_WORK_WIDTHS:



12940    mdlSetWorkWidths_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(S);



12941    break;



12942



12943   case SS_CALL_MDL_PROCESS_PARAMETERS:



12944    mdlProcessParameters_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(S);



12945    break;



12946



12947   default:



12948    /* Unhandled method */



12949    sf_mex_error_message("Stateflow Internal Error:\n"



12950                         "Error calling c1_GCU_Model_genCode_method_dispatcher.\n"



12951                         "Can't handle method %d.\n", method);



12952    break;



12953  }



12954}
